works.description: The Property: Actress Jennifer Aniston’s luxurious Beverly Hills mansion has now hit the market for a whopping $42 million. The former “Friends” star purchased this Los Angeles home in 2006 for $13.6 million, and since then, she has been spending a lot of money to make it a lavish retreat. Mid-century modern architect Hal Levitt built the luxurious home in 1972. The actress was lately reported to have bought a $5.9 million New York apartment.
